{0 day11-test-util}

Shared test helpers for day11 test suites. {!Day11_test_util.Test_util} provides
conveniences used across all day11 Alcotest tests: temporary directory
creation with automatic cleanup, Eio event loop setup, result
unwrapping that integrates with Alcotest failure reporting, filesystem
helpers for directory and file creation, and environment-variable
guards for skipping integration tests when external resources (such as
an opam-repository checkout) are not available.

